Data:
[ Commonwealth Act No. 339, June 21, 1938 ]
AN ACT APPROPRIATING THE AMOUNT OF ONE THOUSAND PESOS FOR THE CONSTRUCTION OF THE ISIRI ELEMENTARY SCHOOL, CALBIGA, SAMAR.(awÞhi(
Be it enacted by the National Assembly of the Philippines:
Section 1. The amount of one thousand pesos appro­priated under paragraph A-(c) ; Samar, item numbered thirty-seven of section one of Act Numbered Forty-one hundred and eighty of the Philippine Legislature is reap-propriated for the construction of the Biri Elementary School, Calbiga, Samar.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved, June 21, 1938.
